Title: Recruiting
Body: MIME-Version: 1.0 Server: CERN/3.0 Date: Wednesday, 08-Jan-97 16:48:32 GMT Content-Type: text/html Content-Length: 2870 Last-Modified: Wednesday, 25-Sep-96 16:47:03 GMT Recruiting The University of Texas at Austin Department of Computer Sciences Faculty Recruiting 1996-97 The Department of Computer Sciences of The University of Texas at Austin invites applications for tenure-track positions at all levels, particularly at the assistant professor level.
